1mNAME0m
       scanpack - scan the source code files within a pack.

1mSYNOPSIS0m
       1mscanpack0m

1mDESCRIPTION0m
       1mscanpack 22mrecursively lists from the current directory and below all the
       files which are compilable source files or include files as interpreted
       by  1mgmkpack  22m,  that  is all files with any of the following extensions
       will be listed :
       "c" (C code),  "F90",  "F",  "f90",  "f"	 (fortran  code),  "h",	 "inc"
       (include	 files),  "sql",  "ddl"	 (odb98 code), "b" (bl95 code), "mnh",
       "MNH" (Meso-NH fortran code).

1mDIAGNOSTICS0m
       If the working directory is lower than the local source directory  then
       the pack content will not be fully listed.
       Auto-generated  interfaces,  and	 more  generally  hidden files are not
       listed.

